## 3. Binding Validation (Phase 1.5)

> Oracle GT 信息 bypass binding，验证 probing 结论能否转化为 accuracy 提升。

### GUI-360 (SFT model, 500 samples)

| Condition | Full Match | Func Match | Δ Full | Δ Func |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| baseline | 29.6% | 62.0% | — | — |
| **redbox** (画红框标注 GT) | **39.4%** | **77.6%** | **+9.8pp** | **+15.6pp** |
| texthint (prompt 加 GT thought) | 31.0% | 66.4% | +1.4pp | +4.4pp |
| crop (裁切到 GT 区域 40%) | 26.8% | 76.8% | -2.8pp | +14.8pp |

### AC (Base model, 500 samples)

| Condition | Type Match | Extract Match | Δ Extract |
|---|---|---|---|
| baseline | 86.4% | 69.4% | — |
| **redbox** | 89.0% | **77.8%** | **+8.4pp** |
| **texthint** | **93.2%** | **85.6%** | **+16.2pp** |
| crop | 56.4% | 45.4% | -24.0pp |

**关键结论：**
- Redbox 在两个数据集上都 +8~10pp → **binding IS bottleneck，修复有 ~10pp headroom**
- Texthint 在 GUI-360 几乎无效 (+1.4pp) 但在 AC +16.2pp → AC 的 step_instruction 极其具体，几乎等于 grounding oracle
- Crop 在 mobile 上致命 (-24pp) → 排除 crop-based 方案

