## 4.5 Per-Sample Binding Correlation (Phase 1.8)

> 不给模型任何 GT。事后分析 per-sample binding quality (cos_sim(target_img, task) - cos_sim(nontarget_img, task)) 与 prediction accuracy 的相关性。如果 corr > 0 且显著 → binding IS the bottleneck（因果证据，不依赖 oracle GT 泄露）。

**方法**: 每个 sample 做两次 forward pass：(1) output_hidden_states → 提取 binding quality per layer；(2) model.generate → 预测动作 → evaluate。

**判定标准**:
| 结果 | Spearman ρ | Binned pattern | 判定 |
|---|---|---|---|
| Binding IS bottleneck | ρ > 0.15, p < 0.01 | good >> poor (monotonic) | 因果确认 |
| Binding NOT bottleneck | ρ ≈ 0, p > 0.05 | bins 无差异 | 需重新定位 |

**结果**:

### GUI-360 (Base model, N=340)

| Layer | Spearman ρ | p-value | Sig | Binned: good / medium / poor |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 0 | -0.007 | 0.90 | ns | 35.9% / 34.5% / 40.8% |
| 4 | +0.042 | 0.44 | ns | 40.4% / 39.6% / 36.4% |
| 9 | +0.025 | 0.65 | ns | 37.3% / 36.1% / 39.6% |
| 14 | +0.033 | 0.54 | ns | 32.5% / 43.8% / 34.5% |
| 19 | +0.046 | 0.40 | ns | 38.0% / 43.4% / 29.7% |
| **24** | **+0.127** | **0.019** | **\*** | **44.4% / 31.6% / 23.5%** |
| 27 | +0.012 | 0.83 | ns | 33.7% / 42.9% / 37.5% |

### AC (Base model, N=500)

| Layer | Spearman ρ | p-value | Sig | Binned: good / medium / poor |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 0 | -0.071 | 0.11 | ns | 50.9% / 61.0% / 48.6% |
| 4 | -0.056 | 0.21 | ns | 55.5% / 60.2% / 42.4% |
| 9 | -0.042 | 0.35 | ns | 54.8% / 60.6% / 45.8% |
| 14 | -0.036 | 0.42 | ns | 54.8% / 62.6% / 50.0% |
| 19 | -0.058 | 0.19 | ns | 56.9% / 54.7% / 59.1% |
| 24 | -0.048 | 0.28 | ns | 56.5% / 57.5% / 50.0% (n=2) |
| **27** | **+0.111** | **0.013** | **\*** | **59.8% / 55.6% / 48.1%** |

### 解读

1. **GUI-360 L24**: ρ=+0.127 (p=0.019)，单调 good(44.4%) >> poor(23.5%)，但 **L27 信号消失** → binding 信号在 late layers 被覆盖
2. **AC L27**: ρ=+0.111 (p=0.013)，单调 good(59.8%) > medium(55.6%) > poor(48.1%)
3. 两个数据集 **最显著层不同** (GUI-360: L24, AC: L27)，但方向一致（正相关）
4. Effect size 偏弱 (ρ ≈ 0.11-0.13)，未达到 ρ>0.15 的 "strong" 判定

**VERDICT: Binding is a PARTIAL bottleneck — 有统计显著性但 effect size 不大。**

- Binding gap 与 accuracy 正相关，但只解释 ~1-2% variance
- 这与 Phase 1.5 的 redbox +9.8pp 并不矛盾：oracle redbox 是 extreme intervention (100% binding fix)，而自然 binding variance 较小
- 意味着 binding 是 **necessary but not sufficient** — 还需其他因素（coordinate regression, action knowledge）

