## 8. Eval Setup Discrepancy Analysis

### 8.1 问题

Exp 0 C0: SFT v2 = 28.1% < Base = 36.7%
Original GUI-360-eval: SFT v2 = 46.9% > Base = 18.1%

为什么排名反转？

### 8.2 Root Cause: Sample Composition

Original eval (19,046 samples) applies three filters:
1. `task_type in data["step"]["tags"]` — 只含 action_visual 标注的 steps
2. `function != "drag"` — 排除 drag
3. `action.get("rectangle", {})` — 必须有 GT bounding box

Exp 0 (26,279 samples) — 使用完整 parquet，无 filter。多出的 ~7,200 samples 包括：
- **3,902 FINISH samples** (gt_function="", status="FINISH")
- 397 drag samples
- ~2,900 non-tagged / no-rectangle samples

**FINISH samples 上 SFT v2 catastrophically fails**:
- SFT v2: func_match=42.1%, **full_match=0.0%** (总是输出 `args: {"coordinate": [null, null]}` 而非 `{}`)
- Base: func_match=67.4%, **full_match=67.4%** (正确输出 `args: {}`)

### 8.3 逐步去除 confound 后的排名

| Filter | SFT v2 | Base | Winner |
|---|---|---|---|
| All (Exp 0) | 28.1% | 36.7% | Base +8.6pp |
| Excl. FINISH + drag | 33.6% | 31.9% | **SFT +1.7pp** ✓ |
| Click + type + wheel only | 35.6% | 32.3% | **SFT +3.3pp** ✓ |
| Click bbox accuracy | 47.2% | 34.8% | **SFT +12.4pp** ✓ |
| Original eval (full criteria) | 46.9% | 18.1% | SFT +28.8pp |

排除 FINISH 后立即恢复 SFT > Base。

### 8.4 Eval Criteria Differences

| 维度 | Original eval | Exp 0 |
|---|---|---|
| Click coordinate | gt_rect (bbox from data) or L∞ 25px | parquet bbox or L2 50px |
| Click other args | ✅ button, double, pressed (normalized) | ❌ 不检查 |
| Status match | ✅ required for success | ❌ 不检查 |
| Type text | 检查 keys/text | 检查 text |
| Drag | excluded (no rectangle) | included |

Other args check 对 base 影响最大：base 经常不输出 button/double → normalized 后与 GT 不匹配。这解释了 base 从 34.8% (Exp 0 bbox) 降到 18.1% (original full criteria) 的 gap。

