## 9. RL as Unified Fix: Theory & Exp γ

### 9.1 Root Cause Analysis

两个 confirmed 问题共享一个 root cause — **SFT 的 per-token CE loss 与 task success 不对齐**:

| 问题 | CE loss 为什么解决不了 | RL 为什么能解决 |
|---|---|---|
| Catastrophic narrowing | click 占 61% → CE gradient 被 click dominate → rare functions 遗忘 | Trajectory reward 不 care action type frequency, 只 care trajectory 成功与否 → naturally balanced |
| Cross-modal binding | CE loss 在 output tokens 上, 不提供 representation-level binding gradient (Exp D 确认) | Trajectory success requires correct grounding → policy gradient 传播到 representation → implicit binding signal |

### 9.2 Exp γ Results: RL Diagnostic on AC (1000 steps, 7 action types)

